{"tid":1481770,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我有野想問香港既貓義工","createTime":"2019-08-17T23:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T12:04:28.000Z","uid":55425,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"547975b968c13137dc368435b4b3d249e9bff27d","tid":1481770,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"我想問下點解領養貓要夠25歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為經濟能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因爲唔夠成熟穩重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁月入幾多先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解單身都唔養得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪驚第時有另一半唔鍾意會棄養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點解結左婚唔俾養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪驚第時有bb會棄養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點解已經有左小朋友既唔俾養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪驚....<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我都唔撚知你地驚乜撚</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我淨係知俾你地撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全屋網窗就裝撚哂<br />\n要咩資料俾咩資料你<br />\n一句不合資格就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔好俾我捉到你濫收領養費<br />\n我實數臭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD貓無人領養你唔好叫人捐錢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為係你地唔撚俾人養</span><br />\n<br />\n叫人捐錢就唔係叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">義工</span><br />\n你係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">利用貓搵錢既乞兒</span><br />\n<br />\n你唔好俾我捉到你棄養個d因為你on9而拒絕被人領養既貓<br />\n佢地有機會有既幸福未來毀係你手上<br />\n而家佢地一世都住寵，無人愛，無屋企人都係因為你地一手造成<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee70f3d328e3a039a4c5a581164c0e0affeabd27","tid":1481770,"uid":21250,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"叫我準備定啲用品，又約上門睇貓，好似好有機會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上門同貓玩緊個時已經講下星期有領養日，會易啲出貓<br />\n問佢今次探貓後幾時知結果又hea鳩我<br />\n<br />\n等左兩日，十問九唔應，最後同我講比左第二個家庭<br />\n因為人地有師奶長時間係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後仲問我可唔可以做暫托家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf55b087541dd543fc174182f44d627ef67e508a","tid":1481770,"uid":291338,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"自己去街執，再帶去睇獸醫仲無咁嬲"},{"pid":"1cf505442f1df98aa74c9fd422730b5a731fce44","tid":1481770,"uid":45242,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"買！！！！"},{"pid":"455610ada770ccda26f24fdea328749f76b95ac7","tid":1481770,"uid":216555,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"買la"},{"pid":"66514dd0a7a5f995f7bf18349171e276fe3b1da1","tid":1481770,"uid":279810,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"bf55b087541dd543fc174182f44d627ef67e508a","tid":1481770,"uid":291338,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"自己去街執，再帶去睇獸醫仲無咁嬲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"冇錯, 係街遇到又唔驚你就係緣份, <br />\n舊區特别多貓仔"},{"pid":"981e525de06e52111f2bb37e11ad27dc626ec9e3","tid":1481770,"uid":8975,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"66514dd0a7a5f995f7bf18349171e276fe3b1da1","tid":1481770,"uid":279810,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"bf55b087541dd543fc174182f44d627ef67e508a","tid":1481770,"uid":291338,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"自己去街執，